    "---\n",
    "## ğŸ¤– Step 3 â€” Initialise the LLM via OpenRouter\n",
    "LangChain's `ChatOpenAI` normally connects to OpenAI. By changing\n",
    "`openai_api_base` to OpenRouter's URL, we redirect it to any model\n",
    "available on OpenRouter â€” no special plugin needed!"
   ]
